DESC:
This presolicitation notice is to notify industry of the Government's intent to negotiate with only one source for the replacement repair and update of the MPN-14K Precision Approach Radar Displays to be delivered to Tinker Air Force Base, OK. The replacement displays are considered to be commercial items.&nbsp;
<div><br /></div>
<div>The inteded source is ARC Technology Solutions, LLC. The Government is pusing a non-competitive action under the authority of FAR 13.501(a)(1).&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>
